<h3>GET /api/projects/:id</h3>
<div>
  Get project
</div>
<b>Resource URL </b>
<div>
http://localhost:3000/api/projects/:id
</div>
<b>Example request</b>
<div>
  curl -H 'Authorization: Bearer auth_token' "http://localhost:3000/api/projects/1"
  <br/>
  auth_token: jwt token of current user
</div>
